                <li>Score if at least 1 scroll is taken</li>
                <li>Score double if both scrolls taken in same round</li>
                <li>Reset board when both scrolls are taken</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>

</div>

<hr />

<div class="table">
    <div class="table-row">
        <div class="table-cell tc-6">
            <h3>1. Deal Cards</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>Shuffle all 52 cards</li>
                <li>Deald 5 to each player</li>
            </ul>
            
            <h3>2. Draft Cards</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>Keep selected card in a pile in front of you</li>
                <li>Draft direction alternates each round</li>
                <li>At end of draft, take the 5 selected cards into hand</li>
            </ul>
            
            <h3>3. Play Cards</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>Start with first player</li>
                <li>Play card <span class="arrow"></span> move disc by amount on card</li>
                <li>Four rounds of play, 1 card unplayed</li>
                <li>Jousts / Tournaments movement cannot be split between boards</li>
                <li>Discs stack, with the newly-arrived disc going on top</li>
                <li>King's Service stops at 12 squares, others have no limit</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="table-cell tc-6">
            <h3>4. Scoring</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>Start with Gallantry board</li>
                <li>Score on turns denoted on scrolls</li>
                <li>Ties are broken with position on stack</li>
                <li>All discs at space 0 are considered to be last</li>
                <li><u>Advanced</u> Before scoring, first player can win a single tie</li>
                <li><u>Advanced</u> Players on Gallantry retreat 1 square after gaining benefit</li>
            </ul>
            
            <h3>5. Reset</h3>
            

            <ul>
                <li>After turn 3, reset discs to square 0 on boards with scroll symbol</li>
                <li>Gallantry, Jousts, Tournaments, Education, King's Service</li>
                <li><u>Advanced</u> does not apply to King's Service
                    <div class="table">
                        <div class="table-row">
                            <div class="table-cell tc-9">
                                <ul>
                                    <li>Last <span class="arrow"></span> square 0</li>
                                    <li>Next-to-last <span class="arrow"></span> square 1</li>
                                    <li>etc.</li>
                                </ul>
                            </div>
                            <div class="table-cell">
                                <img src="~/lib/Images/MedievalAcademy/reset.png" style="width: 50px;" />
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </li>
            </ul>
            
            <br /><br /><br /><br />

            <h3>6. Change First Player</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>Pass Excalibur left</li>
                <li>Move hourglass</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

